             was indicted for <rs id="t17870418-6-off31" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870418-6-off31" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870418-6-off31" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously and feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     <persName id="t17870418-6-person107">
                        David
                         Davis
                     <interp inst="t17870418-6-person107" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17870418-6-person107" type="given" value="David"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17870418-6-person107" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , about the hour of nine in the night, on the <rs id="t17870418-6-cd32" type="crimeDate">9th day of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870418-6-off31 t17870418-6-cd32"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870418-6-off33 t17870418-6-cd32"></join> last, and burglariously stealing therein, twelve printed books, value 12 s. one deal box, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17870418-6-victim109" type="victimName">
                     Francis 
                     Brace
                  <interp inst="t17870418-6-victim109" type="surname" value="Brace"></interp>
